{
  "text": "I have a an observation on archetype one made by Jim. Request comment by Rob. I will read it. The matrix of the mind is the conscious mind and is sustained by the power of the spirit, symbolized by the star, which flows to it through the subconscious mind. It contains the will, which is symbolized by the scepter, power in the magician's hand. All of creation is made through the power of the will directed by the conscious mind of the magician. And the bird in the cage represents the illusion in which the self seems trapped. The magician represents maless with a radiance of being manifested as the creation through which each entity moves. This is slow work but shall make the eventual building of the concept complexes a more smoothly accomplished aware we to have answered the observations as a read by you at this space a time as a much space a time would have been given to the untangling of various concepts as to the building up of what were very thoughtful perceptions. May we ask if there are any brief queries at this time.",
